  "comment": "Light Source\nLamp : 37x25W Osram Led Chip\nSource life expectancy : 30.000 hours\nOptics\nZoom: 3,5° - 55° motorised linear zoom\nLens type: honeycomb gapless plano-convex optics\nColor System\nColour mixing: RGBW / FC / CTO\nCCT: CCT control, + / - green correction, tungsten emulation\nWhite presets: 2.800 K ~ 8500K\nColour wheel: virtual colour wheel with macros\n\nBody\nMaterial : High temperature and anti-UV ABS\nBody Color : Black\nTransport : Two side handles\nDevice Locking PAN and TILT : Yes\n\nHead Movement\nPan : 540º\nTilt : 270º\nPan/Tilt Resolution: 16 Bit\n\nPacking\nProfessional 90 Degree Clamp : Optional\nPower Cable : TrueConwith Cable\nSignal : Male / Female Connector ‘’ 3 pin & 5 Pin\n\nControl\nProtocols : DMX512 ‘’ Built-in Program, DMX, Master Slave ‘’\nShort Mode : 16 Channels\nStandart Mode : 28 Channels\nDisplay : LCD Display\n\nDimmer / Strobe\nDimmer : 0-100% Electronic Dimmer\nStrobe at variable speeds (15 F.P.S at maximum)\n\nDynamic Effects\nColor : Colour mixing mode RGBW\nControl Resolution: 16-bit dimmer\n\nLight Output Beam Mode\n5 mt. : 35.000 Lux 3,5º\n10 mt. : 14.000 Lux 3,5º\n20 mt. : 8.400 Lux 3,5º\n\nPhysical\nIP Rating : IP 65 Waterproof Outdoor\nNet Weight kg. : 13kg.\nDimension : 532mm x 298mm x 434mm\nCooling : Forced Air With Fan\nClamp : Omega Brackets 90 Degree Professional Clamp ‘’Optional‘’\nConnectors : TrueCon+ Signal : 3 pin & 5 Pin\n\nElectrical\nMain Powersupply : 100V-240V 50/60Hz\nInput Power : 925W@230V\nPower Factor : PF>0.90",
